## Alchemy Mini-Game

### Design

Alchemy is the most complex mini-game. It simulates the skill of controlling fire over 5 rounds.

### Fire Control Rounds

Each round presents 3 choices. Choices affect a hidden **Stability Meter** (0-100).

| Round | Name | Choice A | Choice B | Choice C |
|-------|------|----------|----------|----------|
| 1 | Khởi Lô | Tiểu Hỏa (+10 stab) | Trung Hỏa (+5 stab) | Đại Hỏa (+0 stab, +10 out) |
| 2 | Dung Dược | Giữ nhiệt (+5 stab) | Tăng nhiệt (+0 stab, +5 out) | Hạ nhiệt (+10 stab, -5 out) |
| 3 | Lọc Tạp | Ổn định (+5 stab) | Mạnh tay (-5 stab, +10 pur) | Dùng thần thức (+0 stab, -10 Qi) |
| 4 | Kết Đan | Nhanh (-10 stab, +15 out) | Chậm (+5 stab, -5 out) | Cực chậm (+10 stab, -10 out, +5 pur) |
| 5 | Khai Lô | Cưỡng khai (-15 stab, +20 out) | Ổn khai (+0 stab) | Chờ thêm (+10 stab, -10 out) |

### Quality Thresholds

| Quality | Stability Required | Purity Required |
|---------|-------------------|----------------|
| **Cực Phẩm** | 90+ | 80+ |
| **Thượng Phẩm** | 75+ | 60+ |
| **Trung Phẩm** | 50+ | 40+ |
| **Hạ Phẩm** | 25+ | — |
| **Thất Bại** | <25 | — |

### UI Flow

```
/alchemy
  → [Select recipe — select menu]
  → [Verify ingredients — confirmation]
  → [Round 1: Ignite — 3 buttons with descriptions]
  → [Round 2: Dissolve — 3 buttons]
  → [Round 3: Filter — 3 buttons]
  → [Round 4: Condense — 3 buttons]
  → [Round 5: Open — 3 buttons]
  → [Calculate: stability + purity + output]
  → [Result: quality tier + item]
  → [if Cực Phẩm: Đan Kiếp check]
  → [if notable: public log]
```

### Design Rules

- [ ] Each choice shows stability modifier explicitly
- [ ] Each choice shows Qi cost explicitly
- [ ] Timer of 30 seconds per round (BullMQ delayed job)
- [ ] Previous choices shown in result embed
- [ ] Pill poison shown as separate effect
- [ ] Đan Kiếp dramatic reveal if triggered

