## Combat (Auto-Resolve)

### Design

Combat is primarily auto-resolve for this phase. It should be:
- Fast (3-10 turns)
- Dramatic (combat log with personality)
- Rewarding (loot + XP proportional to difficulty)

### Combat Log Format

```
⚔️ **TRẬN CHIẾN — Yêu Thú Đồi**

[Name] vs [Enemy]

**Lượt 1**
→ [Name] tấn công: [dmg] sát thương
   [Enemy] HP: [cur]/[max]
→ [Enemy] phản công: [dmg] sát thương
   [Name] HP: [cur]/[max]

**Lượt 2**
... (repeat)

═══════════════════════════════
🎉 **CHIẾN THẮNG!**
• Thu được: [silver] Bạc, [items]
• Tu vi: +[xp]
═══════════════════════════════
```

### Design Rules

- [ ] Initiative roll shown (flavor)
- [ ] Each turn's attack and damage shown
- [ ] Crit/Dodge/Block indicated with emoji
- [ ] HP bars update visually
- [ ] Victory loot and rewards summarized
- [ ] Defeat consequences shown (injury, death check)

