## Testing Mini-Games

Every mini-game needs:

- [ ] Unit tests for all calculation formulas
- [ ] Edge case: max values, zero values, boundary conditions
- [ ] Integration test: full flow from command to result
- [ ] Balance test: rewards match expected ranges
- [ ] Error test: invalid inputs rejected
- [ ] UX test: player can understand choices without reading rules
